title: Iron Maiden Post 'Wasted Years' Live Video [News]
text:
Iron Maiden Post 'Wasted Years' Live Video It features footage from the "Book of Souls World Tour." UG editor. Music lover. Constant searcher of something interesting and unique. Posted 14 hours ago 
Iron Maiden have posted new live video for "Wasted Years." 
The clip consists of live footage from the band's 2016 "Book of Souls World Tour." 
Iron Maiden will return to North America this summer with Ghost as an opening act. 8 days ago in Community Feed , 3 comments 12 a month ago in Music news , 2 comments 8 2 months ago in Music news , 9 comments Trending stories 23 hours ago in Features , 58 comments 5 a day ago in Music news , 31 comments 1 @ User Post a comment I love how Nicko always looks like an 8 year old who just sat behind a drum kit for the first time.
